        <mxCell id="notes" value="NOTES FOR ECM REVIEW&#10;&#10;• Fargate tasks require ALL listed VPC endpoints to operate in a closed VPC&#10;• ECS Task Execution Role needs IAM permissions for ECR, Logs, Secrets Manager&#10;• RDS + Aurora shown as alternatives — pick one; Aurora recommended if on Fargate&#10;• NAT Gateway only needed if NOT mirroring Tines images to ECR&#10;• All internal traffic stays within VPC; only Transit Gateway provides external egress&#10;• Existing Docker Compose path (Postgres/Redis containers) is mutually exclusive with this" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
